divs: Sighting DetailsAs I walked out of basement this am, I noticed 2 star like objects in the morning sky to the west. I thought they were just some bright stars, then they moved... Objects were very bright, as I watched them they started to move in a southerly direction. ONe object moved closer to the next. As they got closer to each other they dissapeared. Freaked me out. It was like they knew I saw them. They looked just like stars, but they weren't.
